=\"m19.07 4.93-1.41 1.41\"></path></svg><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-moon absolute h-[1.2rem] w-[1.2rem] rotate-90 scale-0 transition-all dark:rotate-0 dark:scale-100 text-blue-400\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M20.985 12.486a9 9 0 1 1-9.473-9.472c.405-.022.617.46.402.803a6 6 0 0 0 8.268 8.268c.344-.215.825-.004.803.401\"></path></svg></button><button class=\"inline-flex h-9 w-9 items-center justify-center rounded-lg border border-border bg-white dark:bg-black text-foreground transition-all focus:outline-none\" aria-label=\"Toggle Navigation Menu\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-menu h-5 w-5\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M4 5h16\"></path><path d=\"M4 12h16\"></path><path d=\"M4 19h16\"></path></svg></button></div></div></header><section class=\"py-12 md:py-16 text-center max-w-3xl mx-auto space-y-4\"><span class=\"inline-block bg-muted text-primary text-[10px] font-bold tracking-wider uppercase px-2.5 py-1 rounded-md\">Get in touch</span><h1 class=\"font-display text-4xl font-extrabold tracking-tight text-primary sm:text-5xl\">Still figuring things out? Let&#x27;s talk.</h1><p class=\"text-lg text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed\">Ask a quick question, or tell us where you&#x27;re stuck. Our assistant can help right away — and if you&#x27;re ready to move forward, we&#x27;ll get you connected to the team.</p></section><section class=\"max-w-4xl mx-auto mb-20 space-y-6\"><div class=\"text-center space-y-2\"><span class=\"text-xs font-bold text-accent tracking-wider uppercase\">Primary Assistant</span><p class=\"text-sm text-muted-foreground max-w-lg mx-auto\">Ask about pricing, what&#x27;s included in each tier, or anything compliance-related — our assistant is trained on everything we do.</p></div><div class=\"border border-border/80 bg-card-surface rounded-3xl overflow-hidden shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-shadow min-h-[450px] flex flex-col justify-between p-1\"><div id=\"assistloop-widget-container\" class=\"w-full flex-grow rounded-2xl bg-muted/20 min-h-[440px] flex items-center justify-center text-sm text-muted-foreground\"><div class=\"text-center space-y-2 p-6\"><div class=\"h-2 w-2 bg-accent rounded-full animate-ping mx-auto\"></div><p class=\"font-semibold text-xs tracking-wide uppercase text-primary\">Initializing Compliance Desk Assistant...</p></div></div></div><p class=\"text-[11px] text-muted-foreground/80 text-center max-w-2xl mx-auto leading-relaxed\">* Responses are for general guidance only and don&#x27;t replace advice specific to your business. For anything that needs a closer look, we&#x27;ll connect you with our team directly.</p></section><hr class=\"border-border/60 max-w-5xl mx-auto mb-16\"/><section class=\"max-w-5xl mx-auto mb-20 space-y-10\"><div class=\"text-center space-y-2\"><h2 class=\"font-display text-2xl font-extrabold text-primary\">Prefer to talk to a human right away?</h2><p class=\"text-sm text-muted-foreground\">Skip the assistant entirely if you already have detailed paperwork criteria.</p></div><div class=\"grid gap-8 lg:grid-cols-12 items-start\"><div class=\"space-y-4 lg:col-span-7\"><a href=\"https://wa.me/2348137941914?text=Hi%2C%20I%20skipped%20the%20bot%20and%20wanted%20to%20reach%20out%20regarding%20compliance%20assistance.\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"group border border-border bg-card-surface p-5 rounded-2xl flex items-center gap-4 hover:border-primary/20 transition-all hover:shadow-sm\"><div class=\"h-10 w-10 rounded-xl bg-whatsapp/10 flex items-center justify-center text-whatsapp shrink-0\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" vie